<Content>Convenient and in budget Very conveniently located (2 block from Zocalo, 1 block from metro). The hotel is clean. Rooms are not luxurious, but they are fine for what you pay. Breakfast not included, but there's a cafeteria beside the hotel. The employees are kind. The only complaint refers to some noisy guests, but that's not the hotel fault. 
